description: TradeDoubler AB engages in the provision of performance marketing and technology solutions. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 250 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2005-11-08. The company operates two business units: Performance Marketing, which offers the technology platform to customers, who want to handle net-based marketing activities themselves and Other. The company is also active in the field of data-driven advertising, via its subsidiary, Adnologies. The firm has geographical segments within Affiliate and Technology summed up to the core business, Performance Marketing and the Region split for this segment is: DACH: Austria, Germany, Switzerland; France & Benelux: Belgium, France, Netherlands; UK & Ireland: Ireland, UK; South: Brazil, Italy, Portugal, Spain, and North: Denmark, Finland, Lithuania, Poland, Sweden. The firm operates Metapic Sweden AB as subsidiary.
naics: Management, Scientific, and Technical Consulting Services
name: TradeDoubler AB
